ing: 2 cucumbers - halved, seeded, and cut into 1/8-inch slices
salt and ground black pepper to taste
des: "This light refreshing side salad uses fresh herbs with just the right balance of flavors to brighten up any summer party!"
ins:
Combine cucumbers, blueberries, feta cheese, scallions, and parsley in a bowl.
Mix oil, vinegar, honey, salt, and pepper together in a bowl. Pour dressing over salad; toss to combine.
